feat.name: Shadowfall
feat.description: Friendly Faction models/units currently in Agathia's control range are affected by Ghost Walk. While in Agathia's control range, friendly Faction models gain Stealth. Additionally, when a model in Agathia's battlegroup ends its activation in her control range, you can immediately place that model anywhere completely within 3" of its location. Shadowfall lasts for one round.

feat.name: Rites Of Shadow
feat.description: When an enemy model is forced, casts a spell, or spends 1 or more focus, fury or essence points except to pay tithe while in Asphyxious' control range, Asphyxious can remove d3 damage points and gains one soul token. If a model casts a spell by spending focus, fury or essence Rites of Shadow triggers only once. Rites of Shadow lasts for once round.

feat.name: Boarding Action
feat.description: Models in Aiakos' battlegroup that are currently in his control range gain +3 SPD and their ranged weapons gain assault. Boarding Action lasts for one turn.

products.name: Captain Rahera, Terror of the Wailing Sea

feat.name: Bloodletting
feat.description: Models in Rahera's battlegroup currently in her control range and friendly living warrior models currently in her control range can immediately make one basic melee or ranged attack. These attacks must target enemy models currently in Rahera's control range.

feat.name: Hell Gate
feat.description: Deneghra, The Soul Weaver immediately gains seven soul tokens.

feat.name: Dark Summons
feat.description: Spawn a unit of Bane Warriors consisting of one Sergeant and five grunts. Place each model completely within 3" of Goreshade The Bastard.

feat.name: Reanimator
feat.description: Remove one or more friendly Faction warrior models currently in Goreshade the Cursed's control range from play. For each model removed, Spawn one destroyed non-character friendly Faction warrior model completely within Goreshade's control range. Place returned trooper models in formation with their original units. Returned models forfeit their Combat Actions the turn they return to play.

feat.name: Winter's Grasp
feat.description: Center 3" AOEs on any number of friendly Faction non-Leader warrior models currently in Goreshade, Lord of Ruin's control range. Enemy models within an AOE become stationary for one round unless they have Resistance: Cold, then the models the AOEs are centered on are destroyed.

feat.name: Consuming Blight
feat.description: Enemy models currently in Asphyxious' control range suffer and unboostable POW 7 damage roll. Consuming Blight damage rolls are simultaneous. Asphyxious then gains up to 7 focus points. He cannot have more focus points then his current ARC stat as a result of Consuming Blight.

feat.name: To The Slaughter
feat.description: While in Karchev & Deathjack's control range, this model and models in its battlegroup are SPD 8. When an affected model ends its Normal Movement in melee with one or more enemy models, the affected model gains 1 focus point. To The Slaughter lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Spectral Legion
feat.description: Return up to 8 destroyed small or medium-based Grunts that were part of a friendly Faction unit to play, placing them completely within 3" of Asphyxious. Returned models gain Undead and Ghostly, become Solos, and cannot be attacked or damaged for one turn. Returned models must charge during their activations and leave play at the end of this turn. (A model with Ghostly can advance through terrain and obstacles without penalty and can advance through obstructions if it has enough movement to move completely past them. It cannot be targeted by free strikes.)

feat.name: Dragon's Call
feat.description: When a living enemy model is destroyed in Terminus' control range, Terminus gains the destroyed model's soul token regardless of the proximity of other models. Terminus gains +1ARM for each soul token on him. Dragon's Call lasts for one round.

feat.name: Vengeance Of The Dragonfather
feat.description: Enemy models cannot allocate focus points to or leech Fury points from models in Venethrax's control range. Additionally, models in Venethrax's control range sacrificed models will not replenish essence. Vengeance of the Dragonfather lasts for one round.

feat.name: Black Gate
feat.description: While in Scaverous' control range, friendly Faction models gain boosted magic attack rolls. When Scaverous casts a spell, reduce the COST of the spell by 1. When an enemy model casts a spell while in Scaverous' control range, increase the COST by 1. Black Gate lasts for one round.

feat.name: Recalibration
feat.description: While in Master Necrotech Mortenebra's control range, friendly Faction models can reroll attack and damage rolls this turn. Each roll can be rerolled only once as a result of Recalibration.

feat.name: Mechanism Of Destruction
feat.description: While in Mortenebra, Numen of Necrogenesis' control range, models in her battlegroup gain an additional die on attack and damage rolls. Discard the lowest die of each roll. Additionally, while in Mortenebra, Numen of Necrogenesis' control range, friendly models gain Side Step. (When a model with Side Step hits an enemy model with an initial melee attack or a melee special attack, the model with Side Step can advance up to 2" after the attack is resolved.)

feat.name: Blood Magic
feat.description: Pirate Queen Skarre immediately suffers any number of damage points. For each damage point suffered as a result of Blood Magic, one friendly Faction model currently in her control range gains +5 ARM and +5 to its Melee attack damage rolls for one round. Pirate Queen Skarre cannot spend focus points to reduce this damage.

products.name: Skarre, Queen of the Broken Coast

feat.name: Fate Weaver
feat.description: Skarre Queen of the Broken Coast immediately suffers up to 5 damage points. For each damage point she suffered as a result of Fate Weaver, one model currently in her control range can be affected by Fate Weaver. An affected friendly model cannot be targeted by charges and gains +5 DEF for one round. An affected enemy model suffers -5 to attack rolls for one round. This model cannot spend focus points to reduce this damage.

products.name: Skarre, Admiral of the Black Fleet

feat.name: Blood Rites
feat.description: Skarre, Admiral of the Black Fleet can suffer 1 damage point to cast a spell instead of spending focus this activation. She can cast each of her spells once as a result of Blood Rites.

feat.name: Dead On Arrival
feat.description: Enemy non-Leader models in Sturgis's control range are pushed up to 3" directly toward Sturgis in the order you choose. Then Sturgis gains 1 focus for each enemy model he is engaging and may make once basic attack with one of his melee weapons against each enemy model in his LOS that is in the melee weapon's range. Those attacks are simultaneous. Then, once this turn, anytime this activation except while resolving an attack you can warp Sturgis anywhere completely within 3" of his current Location.

feat.name: The Withering
feat.description: Enemy models currently in Deneghra's control range suffer -2 SPD, MAT, RAT, DEF, ARM and STR. The Withering lasts for one round.

feat.name: Web Of Shadow
feat.description: Choose 6 friendly non-leader Faction models currently in Deneghra's control range. The chosen models become Incorporeal for one round.

feat.name: Nightfall
feat.description: While in the Coven's control range, enemy models have their LOS reduced to 5". Nightfall lasts for one round.

feat.name: Temporal Flux
feat.description: While in Jezraell's control area, enemy models suffer -2 DEF. Enemy models/units activating in Jezraell's control area must forfeit either their Normal Movement or Combat Action during their next activations. Temporal Flux lats for one round.

feat.name: Broken Earth
feat.description: While in Baldur's control range, friendly Faction models gain cover. While in Baldur's control range, enemy models never have Pathfinder and treat open terrain as rough terrain. Broken Earth lasts for one round.

models.execution: This model gains +1 SPD for each Wurm token on it.

feat.name: Hallowed Ground
feat.description: Friendly Facton models currently in Baldur's control range are affected by Roots of the Earth for one round.

feat.name: Tide Of Earth
feat.description: Choose a table edge and a distance up to 5". Models in Thorle's battelgroup that are in his control range are pushed to chosen distance directly toward the chosen table edge in the order you choose. At the end of your turn, choose a distance up to 5". Models in Thorle's battlegroup that are in his control range are pushed the chosen distance directly away from the chosen table edge in the order you choose.

feat.name: Darkest Night
feat.description: While in Grayle's control range, friendly Faction models gain Stealth. When a friendly Faction model in Grayle's control range destroys an enemy model with a melee attack during it's activation, another friendly Faction model in Grayle's control range can advance up to 3". A model can advance only once this turn as a result of Darkest Night. Darkest Night lasts for one round.

feat.name: Time Of The Beast
feat.description: While in Iona's control range, friendly Tharn models gain +3 STR and ARM. Additionally, while in Iona's control range, friendly Faction warrior models can reroll missed attack rolls. Each attack roll can be rerolled only once as a result of Time of the Beast. Time of the Beast lasts for one round.

feat.name: Wild Mastery
feat.description: Place any number of fury points on each friendly Faction warbeast in Kaya's battlegroup currently in her control range. She can immediately leech fury points from warbeasts in her battlegroup that are in her control range.

feat.name: Call Of The Hunt
feat.description: Kaya can force warbeasts in her battlegroup even if they are outside her control range. At the end of the activation of each warbeast in her battlegroup, you can place that warbeast anywhere completely within 3" of Kaya. Call of the Hunt lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Moon Shadow
feat.description: While in Kaya's control range, friendly Faction models gain +2 DEF and cannot be targeted by free strike. Additionally, friendly Faction models can advance through enemy models in Kaya's control range if they have enough movement to move completely past their bases. Moon Shadow lasts for one round.

feat.name: Blood Rage
feat.description: Kromac suffers up to 7 damage points. For each damage point he suffers, Kromac gains 1 fury point. Kromac's fury point total cannot exceed his current ARC as a result of Blood Rage. If Kromac is in Tharn form when this feat is used, he can immediately take Beast Form. Replace his Tharn form model with his Beast Form model. Effects on the replaced model are applied to the beast model.

feat.name: Blood Rage
feat.description: Kromac suffers up to 7 damage points. For each damage point he suffers, Kromac gains 1 fury point. Kromac's fury point total cannot exceed his current ARC as a result of Blood Rage. If Kromac is in Tharn form when this feat is used, he can immediately take Beast Form. Replace his Tharn form model with his Beast Form model. Effects on the replaced model are applied to the beast model.

feat.name: Bloodlust
feat.description: Kromac immediately casts Carnage without spending Fury. Additionally, while in Kromac's control range, living models in his battlegroup gain +3 STR, ARM, SPD and can charge and make slam power attacks without being forced. BloodLust lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Storm Ravager
feat.description: Place three 3" AOEs anywhere completely within Krueger's control range. These AOEs are hazards. Enemy models in one or more of the AOEs when they are placed suffer a boostable POW 10 electrical damage roll. An enemy model entering or ending it's activation in one or more of the AOEs suffer an unboostable POW 10 electrical damage roll. During each of your Maintenance Phases, remove one AOE.

feat.name: Hurricane
feat.description: Enemy models currently in Krueger's control range are pushed 3" directly away from Krueger in the order you choose. Affected model suffer -2 SPD for one round.

feat.name: Disjunction
feat.description: While in Mohsar's control range, enemy models cannot leech fury, enemy warbeasts cannot have fury leeched from them, and enemy warjacks cannot power up. Disjunction lasts for one round.

feat.name: Seeds Of Destruction
feat.description: When a friendly Faction model destroys a living or undead enemy model with a melee or ranged attack while the enemy model is in Morvahna's control range this turn, center a 4" AOE on the destroyed model, then remove the destroyed model from play. Enemy models in the AOE are hit and suffer an unboostable POW 13 blast damage roll. This damage is not considered to have been caused by an attack. Friendly models in the AOE can each remove d3 damage points.

feat.name: Blood Sacrifice
feat.description: Morvahna immediately suffers 1 or more damage points. This damage cannot be transferred. For each damage point she suffers, return one destroyed non-character living friendly Faction trooper model to play completely within her control range. Place returned models in formation with their original units. Units cannot exceed the number of models they had at the start of the game as a result of Blood Sacrifice. Returned models cannot attack in the turn which they are returned to play.

feat.name: Rites Of The Wurm
feat.description: While warbeasts in Tanith's battlegroup are in her control range, she can channel spells through them. Additionally, when Tanith or a warbeast in her battlegroup casts a spell, reduce the COST of the spell by 1. The COST of a spell cast by Tanith cannot be reduced to less than 1. Rite of the Wurm lasts for one turn.

feat.name: From On High
feat.description: Friendly Faction models with Flight currently in Una's control range gain +2 SPD for one turn. Additionally, while in Una's control range friendly Faction light warbeasts with Flight cannot be targeted by melee attacks. From On High lasts for one turn.

products.name: Wurmwood, Tree of Fate and Cassius

feat.name: Black Roots
feat.description: Wurmwood's command range becomes a forest. Enemy models that become knocked down while in Wurmwood's command range suffer 1 damage point. Black Roots lasts for one round.

products.name: The Old Witch of the Wood

feat.name: Field Of Talons
feat.description: Enemy models that advance except to change facing and end their movement in the Old Witch's control range immediately suffer an unboostable POW 14 damage roll. Warrior models damaged by FIeld of Talons become knocked down. FIeld of Talons lasts for one round.

feat.name: Eye of the Storm
feat.description: When a friendly Faction model makes an electrical damage roll against an enemy model in Nemo's control range, add an additional die to the damage roll. Eye of the Storm lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Reap The Whirlwind
feat.description: While in Caine's control range, models in his battlegroup gain a +1 cumulative bonus on ranged accuracy and ranged damage rolls for each other model in his battlegroup that hit an enemy model with a ranged attack this turn while in Caine's control range. This cumulative bonus cannot exceed +3. Reap the Whirlwind lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Powerhouse
feat.description: While in Jakes' control range, friendly Faction warjacks gains +2 to melee accuracy and melee damage rolls. While within 3" of the affected warjack, friendly Faction non-warjack models gain +2 on melee accuracy and melee damage rolls. Powerhouse lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Overkill
feat.description: After resolving each ranged attack that hits an enemy model, Captain Allister Caine gains a cumulative +1 to his Spellstorm Pistol attack damage rolls. When a model is boxed by a Spellstorm Pistol attack, center a 3" AOE on it and remove it from play. Models in the AOE are hit and suffer an unboostable POW 10 blast damage roll. Overkill expires at the end of Caine's activation.

feat.name: Pitstop
feat.description: Captain E. Dominic Darious gains 3 focus points, then remove all damage from friendly warjacks within 1' of Darius or a Halfjack in his battlegroup. Additionally, warjacks currently within 1" of Darius or a Halfjack in his battlegroup gain +2 SPD, MAT and RAT for one turn.

feat.name: Shadow War
feat.description: When one or more enemy models are destroyed by an attack while in Kraye's control range, immediately after the attack is resolved, one model in Kraye's battlegroup currently in it's control range gains 1 focus point. Additionally, while in Kraye's control range, models in his battlegroup gain Stealth. Shadow war lasts for one round.

feat.name: Firing Squad
feat.description: Friendly Faction models gain boosted Ranged Accuracy rolls while in this models control range, additionally models in this model's battlegroup can make one additional ranged attack during their activations regardless of their ROF. Firing Squad lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Blitz
feat.description: Haley and friendly Faction models beginning their activations in her control range can make one additional ranged or melee attack during their activations. Blitz lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Perfect Position
feat.description: Small and medium-based friendly Faction warrior models currently in Colonel Markus Brisbane's control range can immediately advance up to 3" and then gain Dig In. Warjacks in Brisbane's battlegroup currently in his control range gain Bulldoze for one turn. (A model with Dig In gains cover, gains Resistance: Blast, and does not block LOS. The model remains dug in until it moves, is warped, or is engaged.) (When a model with Bulldoze is B2B with an enemy model during its Normal Movement, it can push that model up to 2" directly away from it. A model can be pushed by Bulldoze only once per turn. Bulldoze has no effect when a model makes a trample power attack.)

feat.name: High Voltage
feat.description: Warjacks in Commander Adept Nemo's battlegroup and currently in his control range are immediately allocated up to 3 focus.

feat.name: Invincibility
feat.description: While in Commander Coleman Stryker's control range, friendly Faction models gain +5 ARM for one round.

feat.name: Dead On Arrival
feat.description: Enemy non-Leader models in Sturgis's control range are pushed up to 3" directly toward Sturgis in the order you choose. Then Sturgis gains 1 focus for each enemy model he is engaging and may make once basic attack with one of his melee weapons against each enemy model in his LOS that is in the melee weapon's range. Those attacks are simultaneous. Then, once this turn, anytime this activation except while resolving an attack you can warp Sturgis anywhere completely within 3" of his current Location.

products.name: Constance Blaize, Knight of the Prophet

feat.name: Divne Intervention
feat.description: While in Blaize's control range, friendly living Faction warrior models gain +1 ARM for each soul token on Blaize. Additionally, while in Blaize's control range, Morrowan models gain Divine Inspiration. Divine Intervention lasts for one round. (A model with Divine Inspiration gains an additional die on melee accuracy and melee damage rolls. Discard the lowest die of each roll.)

feat.name: Microburst
feat.description: Models in this model’s battlegroup currently in General Adept Nemo’s control range immediately advance up to 3” and gain Conductor. (Conductor - When a Stormsmith Stormcaller makes a Surge or Triangulation special attack, this model is considered to be another friendly Stormsmith Stormcaller.) While in General Adept Nemo’s control range, heavy, superheavy and huge warjacks gain Ionization and light warjacks gain Plasma Nimbus. (Ionization – When a model suffers an electrical damage roll while within 5” of this model, add +2 to the roll.) (Plasma Nimbus - If this model is hit by a melee attack, immediately after the attack is resolved you can choose to have the attacking model suffer a POW 10 electrical damage roll unless this model was destroyed or removed from play by the attack.) Microburst lasts for one round.

feat.name: Maelstorm
feat.description: Caine can make a basic Spellstorm Pistol attack against every enemy model currently in his control range, ignoring intervening models. When resolving Maelstrom, Cain can target models in his back arc. Caine cannot use Maelstrom while he is in melee. Maelstrom attacks are simultaneous.

feat.name: Rolling Thunder
feat.description: After all friendly models have completed their activation this turn, friendly Faction models/units currently in Lord Commander Stryker's control range can advance up to 3" and the can make one basic melee attack. When resolving these attacks, affected models can spend focus points to boost one accuracy or damage roll for each focus spent.

models.execution: Tactician [Storm Knight and Storm Legion Models with Cavalry]

feat.name: Lightning Charge
feat.description: When a friendly Faction model makes a power attack, charge or impact attack while in Lord General Coleman Stryker's control range, the attack automatically hits and gains an additional die on the damage roll. Lightning Charge lasts for one round.

feat.name: Thundering Rage
feat.description: While in Maddox's control range, friendly faction model's melee weapons gain +3 POW and Beat Back. Thundering Rage lasts for one turn. (Beat Back - Immediately after a basic attack with a weapon with Beat Back is resolved during this model's Combat Action, the enemy model hit can be pushed 1" directly away from the attacking model. After the enemy model is pushed, the attacking model can advance up to 1" directly toward it.)

feat.name: Breach
feat.description: Remove all wall templates currently in Major Markus Brisbane's control range. Additionally, the next time each enemy model suffers a damage roll while in this Major Markus Brisbane's control range, halve its base ARM when calculating damage. Breach lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Singularity
feat.description: The Models in this unit currently in this model's control range gains +2 ARC and +2 AAT for one turn and immediately gain 2 Focus Points.

feat.name: Temporal Shift
feat.description: Choose 8 enemy models currently in Haley's control range. Chosen models must forfeit either their Normal Movement or Combat Action during their next activations. Temporal Shift lasts for one round.

feat.name: Weathering The Storm
feat.description: While in Captain Athena di Baro's control range, models gain one additional dice on their accuracy rolls and damage rolls. When resolving a friendly model's roll. Discard the lowest die rolled. When resolving an enemy model's roll, discard the highest die rolled. Weathering the Storm lasts for one round.

feat.name: Ride The Storm
feat.description: While in Calder's control range, models in her battlegroup gain +3 DEF, Dodge and Riposte. Ride The Storm lasts for one round. (When a model with Riposte is missed by an enemy melee attack, immediately after the attack is resolved the model with Riposte can make one basic melee attack against the attacking model.)

feat.name: Give 'em Hell!
feat.description: When one or moe friendly Faction models are destroyed while in Wolfe's control area by an enemy attack, immediately after the attack is resolved one model in Wolfe's battlegroup currently in his control area can advance up to 2" and make one basic attack. Give ‘Em Hell! Lasts for one round.

feat.name: Stand And Deliver
feat.description: Friendly knocked down models in Cathmore's control range immediately stand up. Additionally, friendly models in his control range gain boosted ranged accuracy and ranged damage rolls. Stand and Deliver lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Unlocked Potential
feat.description: While in this model's control area, this model and friendly faction models with Journeymen or Junior Warcaster gain a bonus equal to their ARC to all accuracy and damage rolls. Unlocked potential lasts for one turn.

characterabilities: Ancient Mail Of The Grim King
models.execution: Rightful King of Cygnar -  "Any man who has to say I am the King, is no true King."

feat.name: Recless Abandon
feat.description: Friendly Warrior Models currently within Magnus’ control range gain +3 SPD and +3 to their melee damage rolls. Additionally, affected models  can make one additional ranged or melee attack during their activations. Reckless Abandon lasts for one turn.

products.name: Anson Durst, Rock of the Faith

feat.name: Bastion Of Faith
feat.description: While in Anson Durst, Rock of the Faith's control range, warjacks in his battlegroup gain +4 ARM and Brace for Impact. When a friendly Faction warrior model in Durst's control range is directly hit by an attack while within 2" of a warjack in Durst's battlegroup, you can choose to have the warjack be directly hit instead. The warjack is automatically hit and suffers all damage and effects from the attack. Bastion of Faith lasts for one round.

feat.name: Scorched Earth
feat.description: Enemy models currently in Feora's control range suffer the Continuous Fire effect. Friendly warjack models can charge or power attack slam enemy models suffering the Continuous Fire effect without spending a focus point. Scorched Earth lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Wildfire
feat.description: Feora gains 1 focus point for each enemy model currently in her control range suffering the Continuous Fire effect and can immediately give that focus to warjacks in her battlegroup that are in her control range. Feora can then remove the Continuous Fire effect from any number of models in her control range. For each Continuous Fire effect Feora removes, choose one model in her control range to suffer the Continuous Fire effect.

feat.name: Clash Of Flames
feat.description: Feora, The Conquering Flame immediately casts Incite without spending focus. Additionally, while in Feora's control range, friendly Faction models gain Flame Trail. Chash of Flames lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Burnt Out
feat.description: Enemy models currently within 3" of one or more warjacks in Feora The Forsaken's battlegroup in her control range suffer an unboostable POW 13 fire damage roll and suffer the Continuous Fire effect.

feat.name: Strength Of Arms
feat.description: When a friendly Faction model makes a melee attack against an enemy model while the enemy model is in Grand Exemplar Kreoss's control range, the attack automatically hits. While in Kreoss' control range, friendly Faction models can make one additional melee attack during their Combat Actions. Strength of Arms lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Divine Might
feat.description: While in Grand Scrutator Severius' control range, enemy models cannot cast spells or be used to channel spells and enemy leader models suffer -2 ARC and AAT. Divine Might lasts for one round.

feat.name: Godhead
feat.description: For one round, advancing enemy models that end their movement in the Harbinger's command range closer to her then they began suffer an unboostable POW 14 fire damage roll. Additionally, models placed in the Harbinger's command range suffer and unboostable POW 14 fire damage roll.

feat.name: Fires Of Communion
feat.description: Choose 5 enemy non-Leader living or undead warrior models currently in Hierarch Severius' control range. The chosen models suffer a boostable POW 12 Arcane damage roll. If a model is boxed by Fires of Communion, center a 4" AOE cloud effect on th boxed model and remove it from play. The AOE is a hazard that remains in play for one round. Enemy models entering or ending their activations in the AOE suffer a POW 12 fire damage roll and the Continuous Fire effect.

feat.name: Union
feat.description: For each focus point Amon spends this activation, allocate 1 focus point to a warjack in his battlegroup that was in his control range when he spent the focus. Union lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Judgment Day
feat.description: Enemy models currently in High Executioner Sevath Reznik's control range lose all focus and fury points. While in High Executioner Sevath Reznik's control range, enemy models cannot upkeep spells or be allocated focus and those casting spell suffer the Continuous Fire effect. Additionally, sacrificed models will not replenish essence. Judgement Day lasts for one round.

feat.name: Vigilance Of The Faithful
feat.description: While in High Exemplar Cyrenia's control range, friendly Faction models gain +2 DEF. When one or more friendly Faction models are destroyed or removed from play by an enemy attack while in Cyrenia's control range at any time except while advancing, immediately after the attack is resolved one friendly Faction warrior model in Cyrenia's control range can advance up to 3". A model can move only once per turn as a result of Vigilance of the Faithful. Vigilance of the Faithful lasts for one round.

feat.name: Menoth"s Wrath
feat.description: Enemy models currently in High Exemplar Kreoss' control range become knocked down.

feat.name: Resurrection
feat.description: Return 8 friendly destroyed troopers to play. Plae those models completely within 3" of their unit commander and completely within the High Reclaimer's control range. Models that were destroyed this turn cannot be returned as a result of Resurrection.

feat.name: Invocations Of The True Law
feat.description: Enemy upkeep spells and animi in Kreoss' control range immediately expire. Then Kreoss can immediately cast each of his upkeep spells without spending focus.

feat.name: Raging Inferno
feat.description: When an enemy model suffers a fire damage roll wile in Malekus' control range, add an additional die to the damage roll. Additionally, Continuous Fire effects that affect enemy models in Malekus' control range cannot expire. Raging Inferno lasts for one round.

feat.name: Purge The Faithless
feat.description: When an enemy model is boxed by a melee or ranged attack Reznik'scontrol range, center a 4" AOE on the boxed model, then remove that model from play. Enemy models in the AOE are hit and suffer an unboostable POW 14 fire damage roll. This damage is not considered to have been caused by an attack. Purge the Faithless lasts for one round.

feat.name: Call to Action
feat.description: Spawn a unit of Holy Zealots consisting of one Monolith Bearer,  Sergeant and five grunts. Place each model completely within 3” of Sovereign Tristan Durant.

feat.name: Essence Of Dust
feat.description: Friendly Faction models currently in the Testament's control become Incorporeal. When declaring charges and slam power attacks or when making attacks, friendly Faction models can ignore models in the Testament's Control Range when determining LOS. Essence of Dust lasts for one turn.

characterabilities: Elite Cadre [Daughters Of The Flame Units]

feat.name: Shadows Of Urcaen
feat.description: Immediately place Thyra anywhere completely within 2" of her current location. When a friendly Faction model activates in Thyra's control range, at the start of it's activation you can place it anywhere completely within 2" of it's current location. Shadows of Urcaen lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Divine Protection
feat.description: While in Vindictus' control range, friendly Faction warrior models cannot be targeted by charges, slam power attacks, enemy spells, or non-magical ranged attacks. Divine Protection lasts for one round.

products.name: Vladimir Tzpesci, Champion of the Old Faith

feat.name: Crusade
feat.description: Friendly Faction models beginning their activations in Vladimir's control area gain +2 SPD and +2 to their melee attack damage rolls. Warjacks in his control area can run or charge without sending focus. Crusade lasts for one turn.

models.execution: Priest King Of Menoth - "And I will strike down upon thee with great vengeance and furious anger those who attempt to poison and destroy my brother. And you will know my name is the Lord when I lay my vengeance upon thee."

products.name: Agathon, The Voice In The Darkness

feat.name: Well Of Sorrow
feat.description: When an enemy model casts a spell while in Agathon's control range, increase the COST of the spell by 1. Additionally, while in Agathon's control range, models gain one additional die on their magic accuracy and damage rolls. You choose a die to discard in each roll. Well of Sorrow lasts for one round.

models.execution: This model's melee weapons gain Chain Strike. (This weapons becomes RNG 4" during this model's activation.)

feat.name: Shadows Of Annihilation
feat.description: Omodamos immediately casts Locked Horns without spending essence. Additionally, Omodamos and friendly Faction models activating in his control range gains +2 SPD and Ghostly. Shadows of Annihilation lasts for one turn. (A model with Ghostly can advance through terrain and obstacles without penalty and can advance through obstructions if it has enough movement to move completely past them. It cannot be targeted by free strikes)

feat.name: Whispering Void
feat.description: While in Zaateroth's control range, friendly Faction models gain +3 DEF. When an enemy model misses a friendly Faction model in Zaateroth's control range with an attack, immediately after the attack is resolved place the friendly model anywhere completely within 3" of its current location unless it was missed while advancing. Whispering Void lasts for one round.

feat.name: Meta Principle
feat.description: While in Aurum Adeptus Syvestro's Control Range, friendly Faction models gain an additional die on accuracy and damage rolls. Discard one die of your choice in each roll. Additionally, when an enemy model is destroyed while in Syvestro's control range, a friendly Faction model in Syvestro's control range can remove d3 damage points. Meta Principle lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Juiced Up
feat.description: Di Morray immediately gains one juice token and 1 focus point, then warjacks in his battlegroup currently in his control range gain 1 focus point. Additionally, di Morra gains Range Amplifier this activation. (When a model with Range Amplifier casts a spell and is the point of origin for the spell, the spell gains +5 RNG)

feat.name: Arcanodynamic Catalysis
feat.description: Enemy upkeep spells and animi in Locke's Control range immediately expire. For one round, when an enemy model is forced, casts a spell, or spends 1 or more essence, focus or fury points while in Locke's control range, you can place one catalytic token on a model in Locke's battlegroup currently in her control range. If a model casts a spell by spending essence, focus or fury, Arcanodynamic Catalysis triggers only once. A model cannot have more than three catalytic tokens on it at any time. A model gains +1 DEF and +1 ARM for each catalytic token on it. The weapons of a model with one or more catalytic tokens gain Damage Type: Arcane. Remove one catalytic token from each affected model at the end of its activation.

feat.name: Overwhelming Force
feat.description: Friendly Faction models currently in MacKay's control range gain Run & Gun and their weapons gain Damage Type: Arcane. Additionally, when a friendly Faction construct model makes a damage roll against an enemy model with MacKay's control range, the damage roll is boosted. Overwhelming Force lasts for one turn. (At the end of it's activation, if it destroyed one or more enemy models with ranged attacks that activation, a model with Run & Gun can make a full advance.

feat.name: Air Support
feat.description: Put a unit of Crucible Guard Rocketmen (one Leader and five Grunts) and a Rocketman Ace into play. Place each model completely within 3" of Bennet.

feat.name: Fox Hunt
feat.description: Choose an enemy model/unit in Gearhart's control range. Friendly Faction models gain Prey against the chosen model/unit. A model gains +2 to accuracy and damage rolls against its prey. When the prey is destroyed or removed from play, choose another model/unit in Gearhart's control range to be the prey. Fox Hunt lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Metamorphose
feat.description: Models in Absylonia's battlegroup currently in her control range gain +2 STR and Flight and their melee weapons become RNG 2. Metamorphose lasts for one round.

feat.name: Panacea
feat.description: Remove all damage from models in Absylonia's battlegroup that are currently in her control range. Additionally, while in Absylonia's control range models in her battlegroup gain Rapid Healing, Panacea lasts for one round.

feat.name: Field Of Bones
feat.description: While in Anamag's control range, friendly Faction warrior models gain Dark Shroud and their melee weapons gain Grievous Wounds. Field of Bones lasts for one turn. (While within 2" of a model with Dark Shroud, enemy models suffer -2 ARM.) (A model hit by a weapon with Grievous Wounds loses Tough and cannot have damage removed from it for one round.)

feat.name: Flesh Web
feat.description: Bethayne gains 2 flesh web tokens. Then distribute 2 additional flesh web tokens for each non-lesser warbeast in her battlegroup among one or more living friendly Faction models currently in her control range. While a model has one or more flesh web tokens it cannot become knocked down or made stationary. A model can transfer to another living friendly model in Bethayne's control range as if it had the transferring Damage warlock special rule without spending fury by spending a flesh web token. Flesh Web lasts for one round, when Flesh Web expires remove all flesh web tokens from friendly Faction models.

products.name: Bethayne, Voice of Everblight and Belphagor

feat.name: Arcane Symbiosis
feat.description: While in Bethayne's control range, friendly models gain boosted magic accuracy and damage rolls. Arcane Symbiosis lasts for one round.

feat.name: Unstoppable Tide
feat.description: While in Fyanna's control range, friendly Faction models gain +3 DEF and Dodge. Unstoppable Tide lasts for one round.

feat.name: Dragon's Breath
feat.description: While in Kallus' control range, enemy models lose Resistance: Fire and cannot gain it. Additionally, enemy models currently in Kallus' control range immediately suffer an unboostable POW 12 fire damage roll and the Continuous Fire effect.

feat.name: Host Of Angels
feat.description: When a friendly living non-Incubus warrior Faction model in Kallus' control range is disabled by an enemy attack, you can replace it with an Incubus model. The replaced model is removed from play. While in Kallus' control range, friendly soulless warrior models gain +3 DEF. Host of Angels lasts for one round.

feat.name: Rage Of The Dragon
feat.description: While in Kryssa's control range, friendly Faction models gain +3 to their melee attack damage rolls and their melee weapons gain the Continuous Fire effect. Rage of the Dragon lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Field Of Slaughter
feat.description: While in Lylyth's control range, friendly Faction models roll an additional die on attack accuracy rolls this turn.

feat.name: The Reaping
feat.description: When an enemy model is directly hit by a ranged attack made by a friendly Faction model while the friendly Faction model is in Lylyth's control range, the enemy model becomes stationary for one round. The Reaping lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Decimation
feat.description: While in Lylyth's control range, friendly Faction models gain Gunfighter and can make one additional ranged attack during their activations. Decimation lasts for one turn.

models.execution: This model gains Gun Platform and Gunfighter.

feat.name: Troubleshoot
feat.description: While in Mekanolyth's control range, friendly Faction models can reroll ranged accuracy and ranged damage rolls, and their ranged weapons gain +2 RNG. Troubleshoot lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Tide Of Blood
feat.description: Rhyas and friendly Faction models activating in her control range gain one additional melee attack during their Combat Actions. The first time a friendly Faction model damages an enemy model with a basic melee attack during it's Combat Action while in Rhyas' control range, immediately place the attacking model anywhere B2B with the damaged model. Tide of Blood lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Foreboding
feat.description: While in Saeryn's control range, friendly Faction models gain +3 ARM and models in her battlegroup gain Retaliatory Strike. Foreboding lasts for one round. (If a model with Retaliatory Strike is hit by an enemy melee attack during your opponent's turn, after that attack is resolved it can immediately make one basic melee attack against the attacking model. A model with Retaliatory Strike can make only one Retaliatory Strike per turn.)

feat.name: Conjoined Spirits
feat.description: Conjoined Spirits can be used once per game by either Saeryn or Rhyas. When it is used, you can either have Saeryn and Rhyas immediately trade places or you can return one of them to play. You can choose to return Saeryn or Rhyas to play even if they were removed from play. Place the returned model completely within 3" of the model that used Conjoined Spirits. The returned model comes into play with a number of fury points equal to it's ARC. After Conjoined Spirits is used, Saeryn and Rhyas cannot advance for the rest of the turn. If either Seryn or Rhyas is damaged by an attack made by the other, they both lose Conjoined Spirits for the rest of the game.

feat.name: Conjoined Spirits
feat.description: Conjoined Spirits can be used once per game by either Saeryn or Rhyas. When it is used, you can either have Saeryn and Rhyas immediately trade places or you can return one of them to play. You can choose to return Saeryn or Rhyas to play even if they were removed from play. Place the returned model completely within 3" of the model that used Conjoined Spirits. The returned model comes into play with a number of fury points equal to it's ARC. After Conjoined Spirits is used, Saeryn and Rhyas cannot advance for the rest of the turn. If either Seryn or Rhyas is damaged by an attack made by the other, they both lose Conjoined Spirits for the rest of the game.

feat.name: Dark Revival
feat.description: Return one destroyed warbeast that was part of Thagrosh's battlegroup to play. Place it anywhere completely within 3"of him. The warbeast cannot charge, make slam power attacks, or be forced except to cast it's animus this turn.

feat.name: Dragon Storm
feat.description: After all friendly models have completed their activations this turn, each warbeast in Thagrosh's battlegroup that is in his control range can make a full advance followed by one basic melee attack. Completely resolve each warbeast's movement and attack before moving on to the next.

feat.name: Dark Miracles
feat.description: This activation, Vayl can cast each of her spells once without spending fury.

feat.name: Cat & Mouse
feat.description: At the end of this turn after all friendly models have ended their activations, each other friendly Faction model in Vayl's control range can make a full advance. During this movement, the affected model cannot be targeted by free strikes.

feat.name: Phantom Killer
feat.description: Eiryss can make a basic Soulshadow attack against every enemy model currently in her control range, ignoring intervening models, using the Phantom Seeker attack type. When resolving Phantom Killer, Eiyrss can target models in her back arc. Eiryss cannot use Phantom Killer while she is in melee. Phantom Killer attacks are simultaneous.

feat.name: Defiance Of The Void
feat.description: While in Makeda's control range, friendly living models gain Retaliatory Strike. Additionally, when a friendly living warrior model in this model's control range is disabled, this model can suffer 1 damage point to remove 1 damage point from the disabled model. This damage cannot be transferred. Defiance of the Void lasts for one round. (If a model with Retaliatory Strike is hit by an enemy melee attack during your opponent's turn, after that attack is resolved it can immediately make one basic melee attack against the attacking model. A model with Retaliatory Strike can make only one Retaliatory Strike per turn.)

models.execution: This model's melee weapons gain Chain Strike. (This weapons becomes RNG 4" during this model's activation.)

feat.name: Whispers Of Torment
feat.description: While in Beast Master Xekaar's control range, enemy models suffer -3 MAT, RAT, THR and -3 damage on their melee attacks. Whispers of Torment lasts for one round.

feat.name: Death Wind
feat.description: Dominar Morghoul & Escorts and friendly Faction warrior models beginning their activations in Morghoul's control range gain Acrobatics, Overtake, and Unstoppable. Death Wind lasts for one turn. (When a model with Overtake destroys one or more enemy models with a basic melee attack during its Combat Action, after the attack is resolved it can immediately advance up to 1".)

feat.name: Plague Wind
feat.description: While in Rasheth's Control range, enemy models suffer -2 DEF and ARM and -2 damage on their melee accuracy rolls. When a living model is destroyed in his control range, Rasheth can remove 1 damage point. Plague Wind lasts for one round.

feat.name: Arcane Reaver
feat.description: Immediately remove any number of soul tokens, fury points, essence points, and focus points from non-Leader models in Lord Arbiter Hexeris' control range. For each token or point removed, place 1 fury point on Hexeris. Hexeris cannot exceed his current ARC in fury points as a result of Arcane Reaver.

feat.name: Blackout
feat.description: Enemy models currently in Morghoul's control range and LOS suffer Blind for one round. (A model suffering Blind cannot make range or magic attacks, suffers -4 MAT and DEF, and cannot run, charge, or make slam or trample power attacks. It must forfeit either its Normal Movement or Combat Action during tis next activation. Blind can be shaken.)

feat.name: Dark Dominion
feat.description: When a living or undead enemy warrior model is boxed by an attack while in Lord Tyrant Hexeris' control range, you can take control of it. The model becomes an independent model and gains Undead. The model can immediately advance up to 3" and can make one basic melee attack, then remove the model from play. The model cannot be targeted by free strikes during this movement. Dark Dominion lasts for one turn.

characterabilities: Sacrificial Pawn [Warbeast in this model's battlegroup]

feat.name: Scorpion"s Sting
feat.description: While in Zaadesh's control range, friendly Faction models gain +2 MAT and +2 to their melee attack damage rolls and Defensive Strike. Scorpion's Sting lasts for one round. (Once per turn, when an enemy model advances into and ends its movement, or is placed in the melee range of a model with Defensive Strike, the model with Defensive Strike can immediately make one basic melee attack against it.)

feat.name: Dance Of Death
feat.description: Makeda immediately casts Incite without spending fury. Additionally, when a model in Makeda's battlegroup destroys one or more enemy models in her control range with an attack, either Makeda can gain 1 fury point or 1 fury point can be removed from a model in her battlegroup that is in her control range. Dance of Death lats for one turn.

feat.name: Insufferable Pain
feat.description: Naaresh immediately suffers any number of damage points. For each damage point suffered as a result of Imperishable Flesh, one friendly Faction model currently in her control range gains +3 SPD and +3 STR  for one round. Naaresh cannot spend fury points to reduce this damage. For each damage point Narresh suffers from this effect, and 1 blood token up to his maximum of 5.

feat.name: Pain & Suffering
feat.description: While in Morghoul's control range, enemy non-Leader models cannot have damage transferred to them, be forced or spend focus, fury, or essence except to pay tithe. Pain & Suffering lasts for one round.

feat.name: Hide In Sight
feat.description: When an enemy model makes an accuracy roll against a friendly Faction model in Jalaam's control range, the enemy model rolls one less die. Hide in Sight lasts for one round.

feat.name: Rage Of Ancients
feat.description: Supreme Aptimus Zaal gains a number of ancestral rage tokens equal to the number of friendly Faction warrior models that have been destroyed and not returned to play since the star of the game. While in Supreme Aptimus Zaal's control range, friendly Faction models can spend ancestral rage tokens on Zaal to boost one melee accuracy or melee damage roll for each token spent. At the end of the turn, remove unspent ancestral rage tokens from Supreme Aptimus Zaal.

feat.name: Instruments Of War
feat.description: While in Supreme Archdomina Makeda's control range, friendly Faction models gain boosted melee accuracy rolls and cannot become knocked down. Instruments of War lasts for one round.

feat.name: Total Annihilation
feat.description: Whale in Tyrant Xerxis' control range, friendly Faction models gain an additional die on their melee damage rolls. While in Tyrant Xerxis' control range and B2B with another friendly Faction model, friendly Faction model gains +2 ARM. Total Annihilation lasts for one round.

feat.name: Void Wind
feat.description: While in Mordikaar's control range, friendly Faction models gain +3 DEF and Poltergeist. Void Wind lasts for one round.

feat.name: Hand Of The Ancients
feat.description: All models are considered to be in Xerxis, the Fury of Halaak's Control Range. Friendly Faction models gain an additional die on accuracy and damage rolls. For each of those rolls, discard one die of your choice. Hand of the Ancients lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Strength Eternal
feat.description: Remove 9 damage points from each friendly Faction construct models currently in Zaal, The ancestral Advocate's control range. While in Zaal's control range, friendly Faction construct models gain +5 ARM. Strength Eternal lasts for one round.

feat.name: Unholy Communion
feat.description: Choose 9 enemy non-Leader warrior models currently in Alexia's control range. Living models chosen suffer a boostable POW 12 corrosion damage roll. Take control of undead models chosen, which become friendly independent models and can activate normally this turn. Unholy Communion lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Mission Critical
feat.description: While in Strakhov's control range, friendly Faction warrior models gain +3 ARM, Tough and Feign Death. Mission Critical lasts for one round. (A model with Feign Death cannot be targeted by ranged or magic attacks while knocked down.

feat.name: Winter"s Chill
feat.description: When an enemy model without Resistance: Cold suffers a damage roll while in Sorcha's control range, double the damage that exceeds the model's ARM. Winter's Chill lasts for one turn.

feat.name: To The Slaughter
feat.description: While in Karchev & Deathjack's control range, this model and models in its battlegroup are SPD 8. When an affected model ends its Normal Movement in melee with one or more enemy models, the affected model gains 1 focus point. To The Slaughter lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Unearthly Rage
feat.description: While in Karchev's control range, models in his battlegroup gain boosted melee damage rolls and their melee weapons gain Damage type: Arcane. Unearthly Rage lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Howling Wind
feat.description: While in Zerkova's control range, enemy models cannot make ranged attacks. Enemy models beginning their activations in Zerkova's control range cannot run, charge, make power attacks or special attacks, give or receive order, or make special actions. Howling Wind lasts for one round.

feat.name: Undying Loyalty
feat.description: While in Irusk's control range, friendly Faction warrior models gain +2 to accuracy rolls and Tough and cannot become knocked down. Friendly Faction warrior models make a Tough roll of 4, 5, or 6 while in Irusk's control range, removing 1 damage point from that model. Undying Loyalty lasts for one round.

feat.name: Dead Of Winter
feat.description: Place six 3" AOE cloud effects anywhere completely in Sorscha's control range. These AOEs remain in play for one round. A model without Resistance: Cold suffers 1 point of cold damage for each Dead of Winter AOE it enters or ends it's activation within.

feat.name: Poison Pill
feat.description: While in Malakov's control range, friendly Faction models gain Shield Guard and Unstoppable. Additionally, When a friendly Faction model in Malakov's control range is hit by an enemy attack except while advancing, the damaged model can make a full advance followed by a basic melee or ranged attack. A model may only advance and attack once as a result of Poison Pill. Poison Pill lasts for one round.(When a friendly model is directly hit by a non-spray ranged attack during your opponent's turn while within 3" of a model with Shield Guard, you can choose to have the model with Shield Guard directly hit instead. It is automatically hit and suffers all damage and effects. A model can use Shield Guard only once per round and cannot use Shield Guard if it is incorporeal, knocked down, or stationary. The Shield Guard special rule can only trigger once per attack roll.

feat.name: Hour Of The Wolf
feat.description: While in Harkevich's control range, models in his battlegroup gain +3 ARM. Models in his battlegroup beginning their activations in his control range can charge or make slam power attacks without spending focus. A model in Harkevich's battlegroup that declares a charge or slam against an enemy model while in his control range can make a basic ranged attack before advancing. Hour of the Wold lasts for one round.

feat.name: Night Raid
feat.description: While in Strakhov's control range, friendly Faction models gain Stealth, Reposition [3"] and Take Down. Additionally, when a Friendly Faction model charges or slam power attacks an enemy model while in Strakhov's control range they gain +4" movement when advancing as part of their normal movement and Pathfinder. Warjacks in Strakhov's battlegroup can charge or make slam power attacks targeting enemy models in Strakhov's control range without spending focus. While in Strakhov's control range, enemy model's ranged weapons suffer -4 RNG. Night Raid lasts for one round.(Models disabled by a melee attack made by a model with Take Down cannot make a Tough roll. Models boxed by a melee attack made by a model with Take Down are removed from play.)

feat.name: Feel The Hate
feat.description: Each time an enemy model is destroyed in Zoktavir's control range, you can place one rage token on a friendly Faction model in his control range. A model can have up to three rage tokens at any time. Models can spend rage tokens during their activations to make additional melee attacks or to boost melee accuracy or melee damage rolls. A model can make one additional attack or boost one roll for each token spent. Fell the Hate lasts for one turn. Remove unspent rage tokens at the end of this turn.

feat.name: Icy Gaze
feat.description: Enemy models without Resistance: Cold currently in Sorscha's control range and LOS become stationary for one round.

products.name: Kommander Zoktavir, The Butcher Unleashed & Argui

feat.name: Red Haze
feat.description: Zoktavir immediately gains 6 focus points. He cannot have more focus then his current ARC as a result of Red Haze. Living enemy models cannot charge Zoktavir. Red Haze lasts one round.

feat.name: Desperate Ground
feat.description: Friendly Faction models currently in Irusk's control range ignore cloud effects and forests when determining LOS and gain Pathfinder. Affected models currently knocked down immediately stand up unless they became knocked down this turn. Enemy models/units beginning their activations in Irusk's control range suffer -3 SPD. Desperate Ground lasts for one round.

products.name: Vladimir Tzepesci, Great Prince of Umbrey

feat.name: Charge Of The Horse Lord
feat.description: While in Vladimir's control range, friendly Faction warjacks and cavalry models gain Side Step and Sprint. Charge of the Horse Lords lasts for one turn. (When a model with Side Step hits an enemy model with an initial melee attack or a melee special attack, it can advance up to 2" after the attack is resolved.) (At the end of an activation in which it destroyed or removed from play one or more enemy models with melee attacks, a model with Sprint can immediately make a full advance, then its activation ends.)

feat.name: Blood Legacy
feat.description: Choose 6 friendly Faction non-character warrior models currently in Vladimir's control range. Those models gain +3 SPD, STR, MAT, RAT, DEF, and ARM for one round

feat.name: Forced March
feat.description: Warjacks in Vladimir's battlegroup beginning their activations in his control range double their base SPD and can run, charge and make power attacks without spending focus. Forced March lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Hour Of Reckoning
feat.description: The Old Witch gains the benefit of all of her Arcane Machinery effects if able this activation.

products.name: The Old Witch of Khador & Scrapjack

feat.name: Field Of Talons
feat.description: Enemy models that advance except to change facing and end their movement in the Old Witch's control range immediately suffer an unboostable POW 14 damage roll. Warrior models damaged by FIeld of Talons become knocked down. FIeld of Talons lasts for one round.

feat.name: Arcane Convergence
feat.description: Each friendly Faction model currency in Zerkova's control range can immediately cast one spell without spending focus, performing a special action or performing a special attack.

feat.name: Storm Of Ages
feat.description: Enemy models/units activating in Baranova's control range suffer -2 SPD, cannot charge, and cannot make slam or trample power attacks. When a friendly model in Baranova's control range is target by a ranged or arcane attack, the attack suffers -4 RNG. Storm of Ages lasts for one round.

feat.name: Howl Of The Wolf
feat.description: When a model in Borisyuk's battlegroup destroys one or more enemy models with an attack while in his control range, one other model in Borisyuk's battlegroup can immediately advance up to 2" and make one basic attack. Howl of the Wolf accuracy rolls are boosted. A model can only advance and attack as a result of How of the Wolf once per game. Howl of the Wolf lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Checkmate
feat.description: Savaryn can use his Battle Plans three times this activation. Additionally, while in Savaryn's control range, friendly Faction models ignore cover and concealment when making ranged attacks and their weapons gain Blessed and Damage Type: Arcane. Checkmate Lasts for one turn.

feat.name: Hail Of Arrows
feat.description: While in Cylena's control area, friendly models gain +3 RAT and their AOE ranged attacks do not cause blast damage. Instead, models hit by those attacks suffer a damage roll equal to the POW the weapon. Hail of Arrows lasts for one turn.
